THE SCENE GUIDE - LIFE IS A PARTY!


WHAT IS IT?

  "The Scene Guide" (current issue is 1 of 3 in 1997)
  is a fat AMIGA GUIDE ABOUT *ALL BIG* AMIGA PARTIES,
  presenting the  results of the competitions of each
  party and new party invitations, with detailed
  information about each production.

NUMBERS OF THIS ISSUE:

  - more than * 1 Mb * of plain ascii-text
  - 2 pictures
  - 2 modules
  - 223 parties!!!
  - over 1700 productions!!!

WHAT`S NEW?

  What`s new in this issue? - Splitted the guide into 2
  parts (1988-1996, 1997-....); many reviews and opinions
  added (thanks to Jörgen Pettersson and Kenji Irie)
  and of course added much new parties and productions!

